### Root route
GET http://localhost:3000/

### Get all contacts
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts

### Get single contact by id query parameter
# Replace CONTACT_ID with a real _id from MongoDB
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts/single?id=CONTACT_ID

### Render root route (replace with your Render URL)
GET https://your-render-app.onrender.com/

### Render get all contacts
GET https://your-render-app.onrender.com/contacts

### Render get single contact
GET https://your-render-app.onrender.com/contacts/single?id=CONTACT_ID
